tip_battle.title: Sinspawn Ammes & Green Sinscales
tip_battle.message:
• -You'll face Sinspawn Ammes and three Green Sinscale at the same time.
  • -A few turns after all Green Sinscale are defeated, more Green Sinscale join the battle.
  • -Sinspawn Ammes uses Gravity on a single hero or the entire party to deal damage proportional to the current HP of those hit.
  • -Defeat all enemies to win the battle.

  • -Key Strategy-
  • -Use Protectga to raise all allies' Defense.
  • -Use Weak Polka to lower the Attack of all enemies.

tip_battle.title: Sinspawn Echuilles & Blue Sinscales
tip_battle.message:
• -You'll face Sinspawn Echuilles and three Blue Sinscales at the same time.
  • -Sinspawn Echuilles uses the single-target physical attack Drain Touch to steal HP.
  • -Sinspawn Echuilles uses the group magic water attack Blender.
  • -Defeat all enemies to win the battle.

  • -Key Strategy-
  • -Use Shellga to raise the Resistance of all allies.
  • -Although the enemy is resistant to break debuffs, use Heathen Frolic to lower its Magic.

tip_battle.title: Barbariccia
tip_battle.message:
• -Uses strong wind attacks.
  • -Can enter Tornado form.
  • -Uses attacks that Petrify.
  • -Tornado form ends after three turns, or when the enemy is hit with a jump attack.
  • -In Normal form the enemy counters black magic and white magic attacks with Maelstrom, which deals damage proportional to the current HP of the hero hit.
  • -In Tornado form the enemy counters physical attacks and black magic attacks with Lightning, which deals damage proportional to the max HP of the hero hit.

  • -Key Strategy-
  • -Use a jump attack like Soaring Jump to take the enemy out of Tornado form.
  • -Use Esuna to cure Petrify.

tip_battle.title: Demon Wall
tip_battle.message:
• -Uses only physical attacks.
  • -Uses Crushdown after advancing 10 times.
  • -Uses Stone Gaze, which has a high chance to Petrify a hero in the front row.
  • -Can counter attacks with Stone Gaze, which has a moderate chance to Petrify a hero in the front row.

  • -Key Strategy-
  • -After 11 turns the enemy uses Crushdown to Instantly KO a hero, so try to defeat it before then.
  • -Use Protectga to raise all allies' Defense.
  • -Use Esuna to cure Petrify.

tip_battle.title: Reno
tip_battle.message:
• -Uses only physical attacks.
  • -Uses Electrostatic Rod, which can Stop a hero in the front row.
  • -Uses attacks that can Imprison a hero in the rear row in a pyramid.
  • -While a hero is Imprisoned, their ATB gauge does not fill and they are unable to perform any actions.
  • -Attack allies Imprisoned in a pyramid to free them.
  • -If all party members other than the ones that are Imprisoned are KO'd, you lose the battle.

  • -Key Strategy-
  • -Lowering the enemy's Mind reduces the duration of Stop.
  • -Although the enemy is resistant to break debuffs, use Mind Breakdown to lower their Mind.
  • -When an ally is Imprisoned, break the pyramid to free them.

tip_battle.message:
• You'll face Black Waltz No. 1 and Sealion at the same time.
  • -When Sealion's HP falls below a certain point, Black Waltz No. 1 will use Blizzard to recover Sealion's HP.
  • -If Sealion is defeated first, Black Waltz No. 1 will summon Sealion back.
  • -Defeat all enemies to win the battle.

  • -Key Strategy-
  • -Use Shellga to raise the Resistance of all allies.
  • -Although the enemy is resistant to break debuffs, use Multi Break to lower Attack, Magic, Defense, and Resistance.
